# Keep secrets and junk out of the Docker build context. The Dockerfile only
# COPYs what it needs, but the context should not ship .env files to the
# daemon at all — and a smaller context uploads faster.
#
# Patterns without a **/ prefix only match at the context root; **/ makes
# them apply at any depth (e.g. frontend/.env.local, app/__pycache__).
.git
**/.env*
data/
**/node_modules/
.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
frontend/dist/
agent-docs/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
